<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><b>Agency: </b>{!Lead.Company}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b style="font-family: arial;">Organization Executive: </b><span style="font-family: arial;">{!Lead.Name}</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b style="font-family: arial;">Approval date:</b><span style="font-family: arial;"> {!Lead.Approval_Date__c}</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: arial;">Congratulations! Your application for membership at the {!Lead.Location__c} ToolBank has been approved. The information below will help you get the most out of your membership. Please share this information with any staff who will be borrowing from the ToolBank.</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!Lead.Affiliate_Notes__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Here are a few quick tips on how to maximize your ToolBank membership:</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b><span lang="EN">Know the Rules:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><span lang="EN">In your application, you agreed to abide by the ToolBank Membership Agreement and Service Policy. We rely on our member agencies to respect the rules of tool lending and to be accountable. Please read both attached documents carefully, and share them with your staff.&nbsp;&nbsp;Following the rules of tool lending will keep your costs as low as possible.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN"><span style="color: rgb(38, 50, 56); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;"><b>Access to your account:</b></span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(38, 50, 56); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">We will send the login credentials for the tool tracker in a separate email.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;"><b style="font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN">Add Users:&nbsp;</span></b><span lang="EN" style="font-size: 12pt;">You may log in to add additional users to your ToolBank account. This feature empowers your staff to borrow ToolBank tools on behalf of your agency with 100% accountability.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span><font face="arial">Please allow one to two business days for new members to be approved.</font></p><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b><span lang="EN">Take a Tour:</span></b><i><span lang="EN">&nbsp;</span></i><span lang="EN">You are invited to tour the {!Lead.Location__c}&nbsp; ToolBank, meet the staff, and learn how the ToolBank can best serve your agency.&nbsp;&nbsp;Please call {!Lead.Affiliate_Phone_Number__c} to set up an appointment for a tour today.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="EN">We look forward to helping your organization achieve its most ambitious goals. See you at the ToolBank!</span></p></div>]]></td>
